(
<figureCitation id="83AB39AFCE3802036C22FB27679634BE" box="[374,438,1176,1200]" captionStart="FIGURAS 1‑6" captionStartId="5.[95,186,1826,1845]" captionTargetBox="[139,1186,170,1779]" captionTargetId="figure-1@5.[94,1228,170,1792]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURAS 1‑6: 1. Agrilus aegrotus sp. nov. (holótipo). 2. Agrilus anceps sp. nov. (holótipo). 3. Agrilus casarii sp. nov. (parátipo, 7,9 mm). 4. Agrilus crux sp. nov. (holótipo). 5. Agrilus dubiosus sp. nov. (holótipo). 6. Agrilus femina sp. nov. (holótipo)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4656300" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4656300/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="83">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
